2. Peering Connections     → delete web-app-peer, app-db-peer
3. Internet Gateway        → detach from web-vpc first → delete
4. Security Groups         → delete web-sg, app-sg, db-sg
5. Subnets                 → delete all 3
6. VPCs                    → delete web-vpc, app-vpc, db-vpc
                              route tables auto-deleted with VPC
